            "title": "欧洲股市早段上升\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报8,675.52点，升41.77点(0.48%)；德国DAX指数报23,779.93点，升84.34点(0.36%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,880.97点，升27.50点(0.35%)。 (WL)</span>\n</div>",
